summary: An ordinance accepting bid of $505.00 made by W.H. Johnson for all of Lot 3, Block 4, Delmar Park Addition to the City of Seattle, except portion taken for street purposes under Ordinance No. 60250, as amended by Ordinance No. 61848, and for the garage and driveway on said property, and authorizing the execution of quit claim deed in favor of W.H. Johnson to the property described above.
